text:
‘No’: Chelsea Clinton Says She Will Not Run for a Seat on the Senate by Ken Meyer | 9:14 pm, February 11th, 2017 
It would seem that Chelsea Clinton just put a lid on the rumor that she is thinking about following her parents’ footsteps into politics. 
Ever since Hillary Clinton lost the 2016 election back in November, reported rumors have persisted that the former First Daughter was making plans to run for Senator in order to represent New York. On Friday, the younger Clinton attended a fashion event from her friend Tanya Taylor , where she offered a one-word answer when asked if she wanted to pursue Senator Kirsten Gellibrand ‘s seat. 
“No”
